more than $7 million in operating funds. Louise Cummings, the annual fund 
director at the La Jolla Playhouse, has been hired to replace Hall, 33, and 
will begin at SCR on May 14. Cummings, 46, was one of a half-dozen candidates 
interviewed for the SCR post, Hall said. 
