<HEADLINE>
<P>
DENTIST RESURRECTS SOUNDS FROM THE PAST 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By RANDYE HODER 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In the compact disc era, people who talk about spinning some old records 
usually mean breaking out the big vinyl LPs. 
</P>
<P>
