AGRICULTURE; CITRUS INDUSTRY -- RIVERSIDE COUNTY; CROPS; MALATHION; SUNKIST 
GROWERS INC; QUARANTINES; FARMERS; INFESTATIONS; PEST CONTROL 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
