<P>
PRESCRIPTION DRUGS; MEDICAL MALPRACTICE; DRUG ADDICTION; ARRESTS -- ORANGE 
COUNTY; DOCTORS; PHARMACISTS; MEDICAL ETHICS; CALIFORNIA MEDICAL BOARD; DRUG 
SALES 
</P>
