<P>
FIVE-COUNTY COMPARISON 
</P>
<P>
The increase in multi-family home permit activity in Orange County outpaced 
both the local five-county area and the state in January. Compared to January 
1989, the current year opened here with a 67% increase compared to 46% in the 
five counties and 27% statewide. Riverside and San Diego counties both had 
larger increases, while activity dropped in both Los Angeles and San Bernardino 
counties. 
</P>
