<HEADLINE>
<P>
BATTLING THE MEDFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Los Angeles County will conduct aerial spraying of malathion tonight from 9 
p.m. to 3 a.m., weather permitting. 
</P>
<P>
Area: 11 square miles encompassing parts of Diamond Bar, Pomona, San Dimas and 
Walnut. 
</P>
<P>
Precautions: Stay indoors; keep animals indoors; wash animal dishes and toys 
left outside; cover cars; keep doors and windows closed. 
</P>
<P>
Information: Toll-free numbers for the Agricultural Commissioner: (800) 
356-2894; (800) 225-1346. 
</P>
</TEXT>
